50|$|On 22 December 2014, {{the jury}} <b>of</b> the <b>Court</b> <b>of</b> <b>Assize</b> <b>of</b> Liège found four people {{guilty of murder}} of Ihsane Jarfi (fr), {{motivated}} by homophobia. It is the first case in Belgium in which a crime was officially qualified as being motivated by hate {{on the basis of}} sexual orientation.|$|R
